來對面係集團黎 一上庭有十幾人被呃<br />\n好彩個律師夠勁 最後做義工唔洗坐<br />\n其他人就坐晒監..<br />\n律師費好撚金"},{"pid":"d98b638a804bc77cfe828a685a59d6326d9a0351","tid":92053,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:12:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去日本打工啦，時薪一千円</blockquote><br />\n好閪好笑呀"},{"pid":"530064b9bfa4e54175e5a2a57570d7eb8cd445c6","tid":92053,"uid":29799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:12:24.000Z","msg":"係香港地有手有腳唔會餓撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3752dd0150c76aceb05e691c3762c61d08a140e7","tid":92053,"uid":43541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:12:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>賭波？</blockquote><br />\n唔係 最多都係買六合彩廿蚊雞"},{"pid":"46beb030eafbedb6d3281986fcd45a49f1e864d6","tid":92053,"uid":43541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:13:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點問 friend 借 10 皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n分開5-6個人借"},{"pid":"6515bd09112cbe09e23180961ddf1fbeac324619","tid":92053,"uid":7149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:13:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲可以再借多d</blockquote><br />\n我都想搵條loan清左佢 但我入息太低 仲要唔穩定</blockquote><br />\n申請破產 4年後一條好漢"},{"pid":"8f61a8b8a5dd74b1d180ba32854d95bd6b83e1c6","tid":92053,"uid":43541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:14:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主係咪畀人呃左去做保險或者地產果啲底薪都冇既工種？</blockquote><br />\n做過財務狗 過唔到良心 <br />\n如果我肯呃 上連登渣R8果個係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b91fd190160f9b57ab0553491c8bd9dbeeaa0a6","tid":92053,"uid":33336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:15:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif