<br />\nAggger</blockquote><br />\n而加做緊保險狗 好撚想唔做 <br />\n破左就牌都無鳩埋</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係"},{"pid":"bd3827c3a3243374ce7dda9b0c3274afc59a359e","tid":92053,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:19:48.000Z","msg":"依家呢個時勢，求其去做份retail sales都月入15k up，慳啲駛舊錢點會越滾越大？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47135cad0e153d2b5097659e38b9994d15e8d60f","tid":92053,"uid":52671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:20:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>17歲出黎做野 <br />\n做話各行各業<br />\n想努力做Sales工還錢 點知連錢都無飯開<br />\n而加欠落20萬銀行卡數 <br />\n再加10萬朋友債<br />\n<br />\n諗過破產/自殺 但又無勇氣</blockquote><br />\n仆街啦, 2年半年變40萬, 死9緊"},{"pid":"fba08a8972de696b22518f9ab73d6b0a178d0249","tid":92053,"uid":7519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:21:54.000Z","msg":"唸住點還？"},{"pid":"e9f10dc5a300d361205277974cea6bb64a2210a2","tid":92053,"uid":52671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:22:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>30萬好撚多？咁就破產/自殺</blockquote><br />\n我認我貪心 我想搵有爆發性既工做<br />\n但筆數都係越滾越大</blockquote><br />\n做人就腳踏實地少少 睇清個現實<br />\n你肯乖乖地番工一邊還錢<br />\n30萬 5~7年搞掂啦</blockquote><br />\n5-7年, 不如老破, 4年攪掂"},{"pid":"1910f5c8f1767de6564a86f758ef7063be547f7c","tid":92053,"uid":43541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:22:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAggger</blockquote><br />\n而加做緊保險狗 好撚想唔做 <br />\n破左就牌都無鳩埋</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔難估啊 有底薪邊會咁閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e713e1e6762c8c4de7de70ec58dc67ba93c7481a","tid":92053,"uid":43541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:22:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家呢個時勢，求其去做份retail sales都月入15k up，慳啲駛舊錢點會